  <summary date="2019-01-03T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Buy a Brick, Build the Wall Act of 2019

This bill authorizes the Department of the Treasury to accept gifts of money for designing, constructing, or maintaining a barrier on the U.S. and Mexico border. Treasury shall establish a trust fund and website for that purpose.</summary>
